author: Nuran Alteir | The Oregonian/OregonLive
title: Lottery results: Mega Millions winning numbers are...
text:
Another day, another chance at winning the lottery. The winning numbers for Friday's Mega Millions $105 million jackpot have been drawn.
Winning numbers: 25-32-37-45-70
Mega Ball: 1
Megaplier: 5
Winning numbers are drawn Tuesdays and Fridays. The jackpot for this multi-state game starts at $15 million and grows until someone wins.
The chances of winning the Mega Millions jackpot is 1 in 258,890,850, according to the Oregon Lottery website .
